WEBVTT

00:00:42.800 --> 00:00:46.960
Yuxiao Lou is where the world's most capable

00:00:46.960 --> 00:00:48.920
and extraordinary people gather.

00:00:50.520 --> 00:00:52.920
Assistant Director of the Ministry of Revenue, Li Niangu,

00:00:53.480 --> 00:00:57.760
obtained a formula here to boost his official career.

00:00:58.400 --> 00:01:01.280
It is called the Human Pillar Sacrifice.

00:01:02.240 --> 00:01:04.480
But heaven did not grant his wish.

00:01:05.320 --> 00:01:07.480
Not only did his career fail to advance,

00:01:07.920 --> 00:01:09.240
but ever since then,

00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:12.320
he has been plagued by strange occurrences,

00:01:12.640 --> 00:01:15.480
finding not a moment of peace.

00:01:21.440 --> 00:01:22.080
Stop.

00:01:22.200 --> 00:01:22.960
Stop, stop the sedan chair.

00:01:26.080 --> 00:01:26.640
My Lord?

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:27.560
What is the matter?

00:01:28.160 --> 00:01:28.720
Sorcerer.

00:01:28.880 --> 00:01:29.440
Listen.

00:01:29.480 --> 00:01:30.560
There is a child crying in the night.

00:01:45.240 --> 00:01:46.360
Encountering a ghost child at night...

00:01:47.040 --> 00:01:49.000
Does the Human Pillar Sacrifice involve children?

00:01:50.240 --> 00:01:53.440
A living child is sealed in wax within a coffin

00:01:53.640 --> 00:01:55.400
and buried underground.

00:01:55.960 --> 00:01:58.480
Officials pray for a meteoric rise,

00:01:58.960 --> 00:02:02.000
scholars pray for success in exams,

00:02:02.640 --> 00:02:06.320
and merchants pray for abundant wealth.

00:02:10.040 --> 00:02:14.520
What a cruel and absurd superstition this is.

00:02:15.480 --> 00:02:19.480
At the third watch, the ominous wind rises.

00:02:20.160 --> 00:02:23.000
Wax-sealed bones, a soul breaking through the earth.

00:02:23.160 --> 00:02:24.960
Having done such a wicked deed,

00:02:25.200 --> 00:02:28.320
he can only wait for the ghosts to come knocking.

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:35.760
Give me the ball.

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:38.320
Give me the ball.

00:03:01.040 --> 00:03:01.480
My Lord! My Lord!

00:03:01.680 --> 00:03:03.040
He... he... he's here again!

00:03:03.720 --> 00:03:04.240
Who is it?

00:03:04.600 --> 00:03:05.320
Why are you in such a panic?

00:03:06.040 --> 00:03:06.480
It's me.

00:03:07.200 --> 00:03:07.960
Don't you want to see me?

00:03:12.040 --> 00:03:12.680
Interesting.

00:03:14.120 --> 00:03:14.520
Have a sip.

00:03:16.840 --> 00:03:18.000
Do you have any sympathy at all?

00:03:18.520 --> 00:03:19.600
Of course I have sympathy.

00:03:20.320 --> 00:03:21.640
But the person I sympathize with is you.

00:03:22.160 --> 00:03:23.600
You just took the seat of Vice Minister of the Dali Temple.

00:03:24.040 --> 00:03:25.160
If you don't solve a major case quickly,

00:03:25.480 --> 00:03:27.320
won't you soon be stripped of this uniform?

00:03:29.680 --> 00:03:30.160
A major case?

00:03:30.960 --> 00:03:31.680
Of course it's a major case.

00:03:32.280 --> 00:03:32.960
And I suspect,

00:03:33.160 --> 00:03:34.480
you, Chang'an's premier expert,

00:03:34.640 --> 00:03:36.000
have already discovered something, haven't you?

00:03:39.840 --> 00:03:41.200
That is exactly what puzzles me.

00:03:41.840 --> 00:03:43.440
This child was a stillborn fetus,

00:03:43.840 --> 00:03:44.800
delivered over a month ago.

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:47.640
To dig up a stillborn fetus,

00:03:47.920 --> 00:03:48.600
sever its head,

00:03:48.800 --> 00:03:49.760
smear it with dog's blood,

00:03:50.720 --> 00:03:53.000
and while people prayed for children during the festival,

00:03:53.280 --> 00:03:55.680
to hang it inside the crowded Anye Temple...

00:03:56.440 --> 00:03:58.920
By exposing this stillborn's head

00:03:59.440 --> 00:04:01.080
to the gaze of the public in such a way,

00:04:01.880 --> 00:04:03.880
and creating such a bizarre and eerie spectacle,

00:04:06.280 --> 00:04:07.160
this person's motive

00:04:07.320 --> 00:04:08.920
is certainly not just to scare people for amusement.

00:04:11.880 --> 00:04:12.560
Then what is it for?

00:04:13.560 --> 00:04:15.960
To treat a deceased infant with such cruelty...

00:04:17.000 --> 00:04:18.960
this person's scheme has surely only just begun.

00:04:20.080 --> 00:04:20.920
So, what comes next?

00:04:21.640 --> 00:04:22.640
What other

00:04:23.120 --> 00:04:24.440
heinous acts will he commit?

00:04:34.640 --> 00:04:35.000
Husband

00:04:35.440 --> 00:04:36.520
You're finally back

00:04:38.280 --> 00:04:38.960
You...

00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:42.320
Who are you leading?

00:04:46.400 --> 00:04:47.000
No one

00:04:49.200 --> 00:04:49.680
A ghost!

00:04:50.320 --> 00:04:50.800
A ghost!

00:04:51.280 --> 00:04:52.000
A ghost!

00:04:53.040 --> 00:04:53.360
Madam

00:04:53.720 --> 00:04:55.360
It's me. It's me. It's me!

00:04:55.400 --> 00:04:55.920
Stay away!

00:04:56.080 --> 00:04:57.040
Stay away!

00:04:57.800 --> 00:04:58.920
It's me, your husband

00:04:59.800 --> 00:05:00.320
Husband

00:05:01.640 --> 00:05:03.440
The child who disappeared six months ago

00:05:03.720 --> 00:05:04.800
He's back

00:05:06.640 --> 00:05:07.280
Husband

00:05:11.480 --> 00:05:12.360
Stop talking nonsense

00:05:13.120 --> 00:05:14.000
We'll invite a Sorcerer tomorrow

00:05:14.160 --> 00:05:15.160
to perform a Ritual, and it will be fine

00:05:15.920 --> 00:05:16.680
Let's rest early

00:05:25.040 --> 00:05:26.000
An infant

00:05:26.440 --> 00:05:27.280
A stillborn

00:05:28.480 --> 00:05:29.480
Who exactly is it?

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:32.040
What is his motive?

00:05:32.640 --> 00:05:34.920
The first twenty-four hours after a crime are the best time to solve it

00:05:35.040 --> 00:05:36.480
And you still have the mood to soak in a bath here?

00:05:37.920 --> 00:05:38.520
Shentu Baiqi

00:05:39.200 --> 00:05:40.400
Can't you see I'm taking a bath?

00:05:40.960 --> 00:05:42.560
We've traced the source of the stillborn

00:05:42.640 --> 00:05:45.080
It's from the concubine of Li Niangu, Assistant Director of the Ministry of Revenue

00:05:45.160 --> 00:05:45.760
Her name is Hong Xiu

00:05:48.720 --> 00:05:48.920
Put this on

00:05:51.920 --> 00:05:52.640
This is the Dali Temple

00:05:52.840 --> 00:05:53.560
Who let you in?

00:05:54.080 --> 00:05:54.520
Get out

00:05:55.640 --> 00:05:57.520
Last night, Miss Mu and I investigated all night

00:05:57.560 --> 00:06:00.000
We questioned every midwife in all of Chang'an City

00:06:00.600 --> 00:06:03.400
Over a month ago, only Hong Xiu gave birth to a stillborn

00:06:04.640 --> 00:06:06.400
Mu Guiyi is one of my Dali Temple people

00:06:06.760 --> 00:06:07.840
How can you use her without permission?

00:06:13.160 --> 00:06:16.080
The Great Tang's First Uncanny Detective, Master Shentu

00:06:16.200 --> 00:06:17.400
He's my idol

00:06:19.080 --> 00:06:19.720
Shentu Baiqi

00:06:20.120 --> 00:06:21.200
Investigating cases is the Dali Temple's business

00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:22.800
If you act on your own again

00:06:23.200 --> 00:06:23.920
I'll have you arrested

00:06:29.840 --> 00:06:30.640
There is no court assembly today

00:06:30.680 --> 00:06:31.080
Go to the Li Residence

00:06:31.200 --> 00:06:31.640
Shentu

00:06:31.840 --> 00:06:32.800
I'm talking to you, did you hear me?

00:06:32.800 --> 00:06:33.360
I heard you

00:06:33.520 --> 00:06:34.120
If you heard, why do you still...

00:06:34.160 --> 00:06:34.760
So what if I heard?

00:06:35.000 --> 00:06:35.240
You...

00:06:36.080 --> 00:06:37.840
Do experts not need to sleep?

00:06:45.640 --> 00:06:46.240
Acting Vice-Minister

00:06:46.600 --> 00:06:48.360
This is where my unborn child...

00:06:48.640 --> 00:06:49.840
Jin'er, is buried

00:06:50.840 --> 00:06:51.360
Lord Li

00:06:51.960 --> 00:06:52.360
Pardon me

00:06:53.440 --> 00:06:53.800
Dig

00:06:54.320 --> 00:06:54.920
No need to dig

00:06:56.560 --> 00:06:56.960
Why?

00:06:57.600 --> 00:06:58.800
This soil has been turned over

00:07:00.200 --> 00:07:00.920
But it doesn't matter

00:07:01.480 --> 00:07:02.080
As long as he has been here

00:07:02.120 --> 00:07:03.080
there will definitely be clues

00:07:09.600 --> 00:07:10.720
He arrived here three days ago

00:07:12.160 --> 00:07:13.200
How does the Master know?

00:07:13.760 --> 00:07:14.440
Three days ago

00:07:14.760 --> 00:07:15.880
it rained in Chang'an City

00:08:00.360 --> 00:08:01.800
Height, five chi and seven cun

00:08:03.800 --> 00:08:04.960
Regarding his burial here...

00:08:06.240 --> 00:08:07.000
who knew about it?

00:08:10.400 --> 00:08:11.760
Only a few people...

00:08:12.040 --> 00:08:13.080
in the residence knew

00:08:14.320 --> 00:08:15.600
Five chi, seven cun

00:08:17.920 --> 00:08:18.640
Could it be...

00:08:20.440 --> 00:08:21.040
it's him?

00:08:37.360 --> 00:08:38.280
Was it really not you?

00:08:39.920 --> 00:08:41.000
Of course it wasn't me

00:08:41.440 --> 00:08:42.720
That was our Jin'er

00:08:43.880 --> 00:08:45.000
I thought you hid it from me...

00:08:45.120 --> 00:08:46.320
and had someone dig up Jin'er's grave...

00:08:46.400 --> 00:08:47.360
to scare Madam Zhang to death...

00:08:47.560 --> 00:08:48.760
and seize the position of the Assistant Director's wife

00:08:59.080 --> 00:08:59.760
As for me,

00:09:00.160 --> 00:09:02.000
I'm interested in Li Niangu's money.

00:09:03.560 --> 00:09:04.840
As for the man himself,

00:09:05.600 --> 00:09:07.520
I have no interest at all.

00:09:08.800 --> 00:09:09.920
That is good.

00:09:10.680 --> 00:09:11.240
In the coming days,

00:09:11.680 --> 00:09:13.160
Li Niangu will hold a ritual.

00:09:14.040 --> 00:09:15.800
I'll find a way to drain him dry.

00:09:16.600 --> 00:09:18.440
The Dali Temple is already watching the Li Manor.

00:09:18.640 --> 00:09:19.240
If we don't leave soon,

00:09:19.760 --> 00:09:20.640
trouble will arise.

00:09:22.480 --> 00:09:23.640
Could it be that six months ago,

00:09:24.120 --> 00:09:26.240
you used a boy for Li Niangu's Human Pillar Sacrifice,

00:09:26.600 --> 00:09:27.400
harbored evil thoughts,

00:09:28.200 --> 00:09:28.920
and invited retribution,

00:09:29.640 --> 00:09:31.520
causing our Jin'er to be stillborn?

00:09:31.720 --> 00:09:32.440
Don't talk nonsense.

00:09:33.720 --> 00:09:35.440
What matters now is Li Niangu's money.

00:09:36.320 --> 00:09:37.160
As for a child,

00:09:39.840 --> 00:09:41.160
we can always have another one.

00:09:41.600 --> 00:09:42.440
Let's make one right now.

00:09:42.680 --> 00:09:43.920
You're so bad.